Class 10

How to handle calendars:
1. click on the calendar
2. locate the month and get the text
3. if the desired text is not visible -->we will keep clicking next
4. as soon as we found our desired month --> grab all cells from table
5. loop through the cells
6. once the cell value is match with our condition --> click on the match date

Why do we need screenshots in testing ?
in testing it is very important to take screenshots in order to prove that our test case
covered certain functunality
to take screen shots we need screenshots interface

recordings are done manually not with selenium

